200
00:16:12,558 --> 00:16:13,879
All right, all right.

201
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:16,318
I know. You are you.

202
00:16:16,318 --> 00:16:19,839
But it's a place where you can't leave and Qing Mu can't enter.

203
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:22,919
I'll stay here. No one can drive me away.

204
00:16:22,919 --> 00:16:24,478
Must you do that?

205
00:16:24,479 --> 00:16:26,399
Now I'm Qing Mu's wife.

206
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:29,159
Stop. I don't have many thoughts.

207
00:16:29,159 --> 00:16:32,959
If you stay here alone, I'll be worried.

208
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,879
And no one lived here in the past 60,000 years.

209
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:36,558
Apart from mountains, there's nothing else.

210
00:16:36,559 --> 00:16:40,478
If I don't accompany you, you'll be quite bored in the coming 100 years.

211
00:16:40,479 --> 00:16:44,039
So you moved the bamboo house here?

212
00:16:44,039 --> 00:16:46,379
What do you think? Do you like it?

213
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:56,098
