But if you run away blindly, I'm afraid you will miss your chance at love.

259
00:19:15,579 --> 00:19:17,759
It'll be too late to regret.

260
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,699
 Is that your reply? 

261
00:19:45,319 --> 00:19:46,740
 Okay. 

262
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:50,120
 From now on, the tall mountains and rivers will distance themselves. 

263
00:19:50,120 --> 00:19:54,910
 We'll just be common friends when we meet next time. 

264
00:20:01,959 --> 00:20:03,640
Second Prince.

265
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,358
Second Prince.

266
00:20:05,358 --> 00:20:06,879
You haven't been here for a long time.

267
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,818
Let me tell Master.

268
00:20:08,818 --> 00:20:10,500
No, thanks.

269
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:12,379
I'm here to see Qing Mu.

270
00:20:15,359 --> 00:20:17,120
Look at my memory.

271
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:20,190
Qing Mu has gone to the Human Realm to clean evil aura.

272
00:20:20,190 --> 00:20:21,779
I will visit again another day.

273
00:20:21,779 --> 00:20:23,500
Second Prince.

274
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:26,198
Since you have come, have some tea.

275
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:30,500
Or Master will say that I do not understand the etiquette of hospitality.

276
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:33,438
I have other things to do.

277
00:20:33,439 --> 00:20:35,919
I'll visit him another day.

278
00:20:35,919 --> 00:20:37,779
Farewell.

279
00:20:37,779 --> 00:20:39,179
Yes.

280
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,958
Strange.

281
00:20:41,958 --> 00:20:44,799
You said you're here to see Qing Mu.

282
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:46,919
But in fact, you want to see Feng Ran.

283
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:48,478
No.

284
00:20:48,479 --> 00:20:50,339
I have to report.

285
00:21:04,199 --> 00:21:05,478
Lordess Feng Ran.

286
00:21:05,479 --> 00:21:07,039
Since you have returned from the Human Realm,

287
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,679
you've been practicing sword skills.

288
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:11,219
I'm going to die if you don't get tired.

289
00:21:13,700 --> 00:21:14,838
Lordess.

290
00:21:14,839 --> 00:21:16,379
Lordess.

291
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:21,298
Lordess, Prince Jing Jian has come to Qingchi Palace.

292
00:21:21,298 --> 00:21:23,080
Really?

293
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,539
I won't see him.

294
00:21:25,539 --> 00:21:28,099
He has already left.

295
00:21:28,099 --> 00:21:29,939
He left?

296
00:21:29,939 --> 00:21:31,578
Where did you see him?

297
00:21:31,578 --> 00:21:33,510
Outside of the gate,

298
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:36,050
he said he came to see Qing Mu.

299
00:21:36,050 --> 00:21:38,318
I invited him to have some tea, but he refused

300
00:21:38,319 --> 00:21:40,039
and said he would come another day.

301
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:44,279
Qing Mu said Jing Jian was going to see him off today.

302
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:46,078
What a crappy excuse!

303
00:21:46,079 --> 00:21:47,858
I hate his hesitant nature the most.

304
00:21:47,858 --> 00:21:50,119
I'll never forgive him.

305
00:21:50,719 --> 00:21:55,239
Lordess, did you break up with him?

306
00:21:57,020 --> 00:22:01,179
No wonder you just practice and eat nothing these days.

307
00:22:01,179 --> 00:22:03,518
Shut up. I have nothing to do with him.

308
00:22:03,518 --> 00:22:05,478
You are not allowed to mention him in front of me from now on.

309
00:22:05,479 --> 00:22:07,060
If you mention him once more,

310
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:09,710
I'll cut off your tongues. You can leave!

311
00:22:09,710 --> 00:22:11,259
Yes.

312
00:22:12,839 --> 00:22:14,718
- Wait for me. 
 - Hurry up.

313
00:22:15,959 --> 00:22:19,838
Who is so powerful that they have annoyed Lordess Feng Ran?

314
00:22:19,839 --> 00:22:21,439
Upper God.

315
00:22:24,179 --> 00:22:26,218
Upper God, don't tease me.

316
00:22:26,218 --> 00:22:28,298
We don't have a good relationship with Heavenly Palace.

317
00:22:28,298 --> 00:22:32,259
Those who come from the Heavenly Palace won't be allowed to enter Qingchi Palace.

318
00:22:32,259 --> 00:22:34,110
I never considered Jing Jian the same

319
00:22:34,110 --> 00:22:36,950
as other people in the Heavenly Palace.

320
00:22:36,950 --> 00:22:40,250
Jing Jian is kind.

321
00:22:40,250 --> 00:22:42,198
He's respectable.

322
00:22:42,199 --> 00:22:46,220
If he wants to come to Qingchi Palace, I'll welcome him.

323
00:22:46,220 --> 00:22:48,399
Upper God, don't oppose me.

324
00:22:48,399 --> 00:22:50,030
Where is he righteous and kind?

325
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:54,630
Obviously, he is duplicitous and inflexible.

326
00:22:54,630 --> 00:22:59,280
Emotional entanglement can't be untied by anger.

327
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:01,958
Jing Jian is the second prince of Heavenly Palace.

328
00:23:01,959 --> 00:23:04,480
He has a heavy responsibility.

329
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:11,200
How can he be worthy of his status if he only has love in his eyes?

330
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:15,718
Besides, Heavenly Palace and Qingchi Palace have never been on good terms with each other.

331
00:23:15,718 --> 00:23:17,838
And you have a feud with Jing Yang.

332
00:23:17,900 --> 00:23:24,300
Wouldn't it be sloppy for him to make a promise to you easily regardless of his position?

333
00:23:24,319 --> 00:23:26,340
But he...

334
00:23:26,340 --> 00:23:28,558
Come on. Trust me.

335
00:23:28,558 --> 00:23:31,160
I think he is thoughtful

336
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:33,870
and worthy of your trust for life.

337
00:23:33,870 --> 00:23:36,040
Think about it again.

338
00:24:14,760 --> 00:24:18,238
 To this day, you are still confusing right and wrong. 

339
00:24:18,239 --> 00:24:21,260
 60,000 years ago, you killed Yue... 

340
00:24:29,060 --> 00:24:31,899
 Demon God hasn't recovered his True God power. 

341
00:24:31,899 --> 00:24:34,880
 But he'll find me and get revenge for Yue Mi. 

342
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:39,170
 Getting stronger is my only way out. 

343
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:59,519
You said you were good at cooking.

344
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:02,538
Mr. Demon God, you almost ruined the house.

345
00:25:02,538 --> 00:25:05,539
How has Xuanjing Palace held up till today?

346
00:25:05,539 --> 00:25:08,118
It's ruined, but we can build a new one.

347
00:25:08,119 --> 00:25:10,418
When the smoke is gone, let me try again.

348
00:25:10,418 --> 00:25:12,078
You want to try again?

349
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:14,919
If you continue like this, I won't survive 100 years.

350
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,198
How could that do?

351
00:25:16,199 --> 00:25:18,118
I said I would take care of your diet and daily life.

352
00:25:18,119 --> 00:25:20,599
Cooking is a must.

353
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:23,079
Let me cook.

354
00:25:24,479 --> 00:25:27,118
How can that work? I said I was here to accompany you.

355
00:25:27,118 --> 00:25:29,379
I won't let you get tired.

356
00:25:29,379 --> 00:25:31,740
Fortunately, I'm smart.

357
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:34,399
Even Qing Mu hasn't tasted the food cooked by Hou Chi.

358
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:36,560
I get to eat it first.

359
00:25:50,839 --> 00:25:54,119
What's Qing Mu doing now?

360
00:26:18,319 --> 00:26:19,519
It's you.

361
00:26:19,519 --> 00:26:22,580
You followed me in the six cities in the Human Realm.

362
00:26:24,660 --> 00:26:27,880
You don't have to be worried that I'll disclose

363
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:28,950
Jing Yang's crime.

364
00:26:28,950 --> 00:26:31,779
Hou Chi has asked Jing Jian to make the decision.

365
00:26:31,779 --> 00:26:33,858
And I won't oppose. Princess, you should leave.

366
00:26:33,858 --> 00:26:35,859
Qing Mu, I...

367
00:26:38,079 --> 00:26:40,219
I just wanted to thank you.

368
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:47,200
Can't you and I get along like friends?

369
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:50,660
You will always be the third princess of the Heavenly Palace to me.

370
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:52,399
I'm going to clean the evil auras.

371
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:54,078
I can't miss a moment.

372
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:56,479
Don't follow me anymore.

373
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:25,838
Though there's huge stress in Shenyin Mountain,

374
00:27:25,839 --> 00:27:28,159
a lot of fairy grass grows here.

375
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:31,700
I can collect some as medicine refining materials for Chang Que.

376
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:43,469
I didn't expect Di Xiu, a magic herb in ancient times, to be here.

377
00:27:43,469 --> 00:27:46,118
"The Classic of Mountains and Seas" says it has yellow flowers and black fruits.

378
00:27:46,119 --> 00:27:48,799
People will calm down and forget unhappiness after having it.

379
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:51,820
I'll give it to Qing Mu.

380
00:27:58,719 --> 00:28:01,439
Is there any letter from Qing Mu?

381
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:07,258
 My wife, Hou Chi, I miss you. 

382
00:28:08,420 --> 00:28:10,790
 We haven't seen each other for two years. 

383
00:28:10,790 --> 00:28:15,040
 Have you had a good life on Shenyin Mountain? 

384
00:28:15,959 --> 00:28:18,640
 It is late autumn in Dibei City. 

385
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:20,138
 Shuo'er has grown up. 

386
00:28:20,138 --> 00:28:24,579
 ♫ Year after year time goes by ♫ 

387
00:28:24,580 --> 00:28:31,359
 ♫ Don't be afraid if our fate comes back ♫ 

388
00:28:31,359 --> 00:28:34,198
 ♫ Rains flood and memories last ♫ 

389
00:28:34,199 --> 00:28:38,639
 In the last letter you mentioned about Jing Yuan, I was anxious and couldn't sleep. 

390
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:44,010
 While cleaning evil aura, I took the chance to ask the demons. 

391
00:28:44,010 --> 00:28:47,760
 ♫ I have been waiting for so many years ♫ 

392
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:49,679
 Chang Qin told me, 

393
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:53,040
 though Demon God has strong power, he also has a weakness. 

394
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:56,819
 He's poor at drinking wine. 

395
00:28:56,819 --> 00:28:59,318
 If he bothers you on Shenyin Mountain, 

396
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:04,600
 use the wine recipe I gave you to make him sleep for days so that you'll get some peace. 

397
00:29:04,689 --> 00:29:11,490
 ♫ I'll wait through my lifetime ♫ 

398
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:23,059
 I've tried your recipe. 

399
00:29:23,059 --> 00:29:26,950
 Instead of sleeping, he has diarrhea. 

400
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:28,198
 I have not seen you in two years. 

401
00:29:28,199 --> 00:29:31,740
 Unexpectedly, Lord Qing Mu, you're still naive. 

402
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:36,299
 Hou Chi, when you receive this letter, 

403
00:29:36,299 --> 00:29:39,399
 I've arrived in the city near the North Sea. 

404
00:29:39,399 --> 00:29:42,019
 It's said that the hawthorns here are delicious. 

405
00:29:42,019 --> 00:29:45,160
 I'll buy you some. 

406
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:48,899
 ♫ I spend years waiting for returning birds ♫ 

407
00:29:48,900 --> 00:29:52,559
 ♫ I never regret it and no one can replace you ♫ 

408
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:59,960
 ♫ I hope we'll uncover the past when we wake up ♫ 

409
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:02,759
 Shenyin Mountain has beautiful landscapes. 

410
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:06,118
 If there is a chance, I really want to see it with you. 

411
00:30:06,119 --> 00:30:10,978
 I've started cleaning evil auras with my power according to your map. 

412
00:30:10,978 --> 00:30:15,498
 But I'm worried that you may face danger outside. 

413
00:30:15,498 --> 00:30:19,119
 Take good care of yourself and don't make me worried. 

414
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:28,200
 ♫ Tears turn into clouds and rain falls in my heart ♫ 

415
00:30:28,218 --> 00:30:33,659
 Hou Chi, 100 years are so long for me. 

416
00:30:34,750 --> 00:30:44,450
 ♫ I'll enjoy a free life with you forever ♫ 

417
00:30:57,479 --> 00:31:00,418
Yang'er? How is it possible?

418
00:31:00,418 --> 00:31:01,718
Calm down.

419
00:31:01,719 --> 00:31:03,819
It's just my speculation.

420
00:31:03,819 --> 00:31:05,700
I still need verification.

421
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:11,478
Because Wu Huan was banished to the Netherworld, Yang'er has long been heartbroken.

422
00:31:11,479 --> 00:31:14,919
But if he has anything to do with the evil auras in the Human Realm and Bi Xi's disappearance,

423
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,819
I will give him punishment.

424
00:31:17,719 --> 00:31:20,938
Heavenly King is fair. Your justice is our fortune.

425
00:31:20,938 --> 00:31:24,480
But there's another thing for you to make a judgment on.

426
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:29,738
Immortals and demons have been fighting in the Luocha Region.

427
00:31:29,738 --> 00:31:33,018
The Demon Clan keep saying that their clansmen were being taken away by the Heavenly Palace.

428
00:31:33,018 --> 00:31:37,419
At first, I thought they were lying to stir up trouble.

429
00:31:37,419 --> 00:31:40,759
But I happened to discover these criminals

430
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:43,699
that should have been imprisoned somewhere in the Immortal Realm.

431
00:31:43,699 --> 00:31:45,800
They died a terrible death.

432
00:31:49,979 --> 00:31:52,279
Spiritual power exhausted.

433
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:54,059
Dried figure and appearance.

434
00:31:54,059 --> 00:31:55,700
Evil auras.

435
00:31:58,079 --> 00:32:01,498
Although the devils were eliminated by the gods 60,000 years ago,

436
00:32:01,498 --> 00:32:04,598
resentment aura, sin aura, and evil aura can lead to more devils.

437
00:32:04,599 --> 00:32:08,238
If this war criminal really escaped from the Heavenly Palace,

438
00:32:08,239 --> 00:32:10,459
then he must have something to do with the palace.

439
00:32:10,459 --> 00:32:13,258
Dong Hua, it's a big matter.

440
00:32:13,258 --> 00:32:16,520
Don't leak it until you find it out.

441
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:20,859
Don't worry. I will keep my mouth shut.

442
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,839
Father God, you sent urgent orders for me to come in a hurry.

443
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:39,839
Is there anything wrong with the Luocha Region?

444
00:32:40,479 --> 00:32:41,838
Don't worry.

445
00:32:41,839 --> 00:32:44,358
I called you here not for war.

446
00:32:44,359 --> 00:32:47,100
I want you to go to Wutong Forest.

447
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:48,800
Wutong Forest?

448
00:32:50,479 --> 00:32:56,598
Before Feng Yun died, he passed the throne of patriarch to your mother.

449
00:32:56,599 --> 00:33:00,679
As the patriarch, your mother has now been secluded to the Netherworld for 100 years.

450
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:03,098
The Phoenix Clan needs someone to deal with their affairs.

451
00:33:03,098 --> 00:33:04,539
You're also a phoenix.

452
00:33:04,539 --> 00:33:07,400
You should takeover the seal of the patriarch for the clan.

453
00:33:08,199 --> 00:33:11,438
Father, I'm inexperienced.

454
00:33:11,438 --> 00:33:15,360
By the way, though my mother is in the Netherworld, she'll return soon.

455
00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:17,958
I've made the decision.

456
00:33:17,959 --> 00:33:19,779
Don't say more.

457
00:33:19,779 --> 00:33:21,498
You're the son of the Heavenly King.

458
00:33:21,498 --> 00:33:23,318
I think it's a good idea.

459
00:33:23,319 --> 00:33:24,799
You should leave.

460
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:26,239
Yes.

461
00:33:43,439 --> 00:33:46,838
What? His Majesty asked Jian'er to be the patriarch?

462
00:33:46,838 --> 00:33:49,779
Queen, you're dedicated to the Phoenix Clan.

463
00:33:49,779 --> 00:33:52,118
But Jing Jian is your son.

464
00:33:52,119 --> 00:33:55,080
Why not let him be in charge of the affairs?

465
00:33:56,959 --> 00:33:58,619
I've misspoken.

466
00:34:02,520 --> 00:34:09,119
I can tell you that I have some secrets hidden in Wutong Forest.

467
00:34:09,120 --> 00:34:11,139
I don't want Jian'er to know of them.

468
00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:15,559
How did you take advantage of those demon soldiers?

469
00:34:15,560 --> 00:34:18,020
I followed your orders well.

470
00:34:23,719 --> 00:34:26,618
This elixir pill contains a lot of spiritual power of demon soldiers.

471
00:34:26,618 --> 00:34:28,920
It can help you clean the evil auras.

472
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:37,279
Due to my carelessness,

473
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,979
the evil auras invaded my body.

474
00:34:39,979 --> 00:34:42,738
If one step is wrong, then every step will be wrong.

475
00:34:42,738 --> 00:34:49,198
Now I have no choice but to absorb a lot of spiritual power to clean the evil auras.

476
00:34:49,199 --> 00:34:50,438
Don't worry.

477
00:34:50,439 --> 00:34:53,920
I'll find more power for you.

478
00:34:56,399 --> 00:34:58,799
Since I took charge of the Phoenix Clan,

479
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:01,058
there has not been a day when I have not done my best.

480
00:35:01,058 --> 00:35:04,839
During the past 60,000 years,

481
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:07,559
my followers in Wutong Forest sing praises to me for my protection.

482
00:35:08,399 --> 00:35:13,019
Now it's time that they should repay.

483
00:35:13,019 --> 00:35:17,759
You want to sacrifice the Phoenix Clan?

484
00:35:18,499 --> 00:35:20,438
No one has had a position as high as mine

485
00:35:20,439 --> 00:35:23,178
since the phoenixes appeared thousands of years ago.

486
00:35:23,178 --> 00:35:26,079
If I become a devil, they'll be ashamed.

487
00:35:26,080 --> 00:35:28,359
And we won't get recognized in the three realms.

488
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,799
Compared with honor,

489
00:35:29,799 --> 00:35:32,959
hundreds of lives are nothing.

490
00:35:34,399 --> 00:35:36,080
Queen.

491
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,920
You've followed me for hundreds of years.

492
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:47,050
If any of my crimes are disclosed,

493
00:35:47,050 --> 00:35:49,850
you won't be able to run away from responsibility.

494
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:52,899
I see.

495
00:35:55,959 --> 00:35:58,699
How is Elder Dan Feng recently?

496
00:35:58,699 --> 00:36:00,379
Nothing has changed.

497
00:36:00,379 --> 00:36:01,899
She's crazy all day long.

498
00:36:01,899 --> 00:36:04,560
It's said that she'll die.

499
00:36:19,479 --> 00:36:23,478
My spirit is attached to this instruction feather.

500
00:36:23,479 --> 00:36:28,079
Hand it to Elder Dan Feng.

501
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:29,478
Are you going to...

502
00:36:29,479 --> 00:36:34,379
I want to clean the evil auras and keep the secret of the Wutong Forest.

503
00:36:35,040 --> 00:36:37,219
I have no choice.

504
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:39,680
Yes.

505
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,599
Impossible.

506
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:13,718
I've cooked it several times.

507
00:37:13,719 --> 00:37:15,079
Though I don't cook as well as you,

508
00:37:15,080 --> 00:37:16,718
it shouldn't be so terrible.

509
00:37:16,719 --> 00:37:20,279
It's my fault, I had too much in the morning.

510
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,839
Perhaps I'm stuffed.

511
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:23,459
Come on. Have some fish.

512
00:37:23,459 --> 00:37:25,839
Fish from the river is the freshest.

513
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,698
Come on. Let me feed you.

514
00:37:32,239 --> 00:37:33,519
Hou Chi,

515
00:37:33,520 --> 00:37:36,320
though you have poor power, you're also an immortal.

516
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:38,599
Why is it like a mortal body now?

517
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:40,700
Did something happen?

518
00:37:51,180 --> 00:37:54,740
Why do I have such power?

519
00:37:58,399 --> 00:38:00,179
Silver and red.

520
00:38:00,179 --> 00:38:03,759
Hou Chi, are you pregnant?

521
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:10,999
Hou Chi,

522
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:16,858
having a baby after marriage is natural.

523
00:38:16,858 --> 00:38:18,718
Though we're not in the Human Realm,

524
00:38:18,719 --> 00:38:20,500
you shouldn't...

525
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:23,920
Hou Chi.

526
00:38:26,959 --> 00:38:29,279
Hou Chi! Hou Chi!

527
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:06,039
Shall we keep this secret and tell Qing Mu face to face?

528
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:20,439
Strange.

529
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:22,478
Normally, all the birds in Wutong Forest are singing.

530
00:39:22,479 --> 00:39:24,560
Why is it so quiet?

531
00:39:31,639 --> 00:39:33,279
Oh no!

532
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:34,999
Something has happened to the Phoenix Clan.

533
00:39:40,080 --> 00:39:41,439
Feng Ran?

534
00:39:44,479 --> 00:39:46,978
Why are you here? My bad luck.

535
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:51,459
You're not hurt. You shall leave.

536
00:39:51,459 --> 00:39:53,400
I'm afraid there's something wrong.

537
00:39:55,639 --> 00:39:58,699
I don't know where Lordess Feng Ran got the news.

538
00:39:58,699 --> 00:40:01,198
Mind your words. Behave normally.

539
00:40:04,439 --> 00:40:06,539
Forget it.  I really don't know you in general.

540
00:40:06,539 --> 00:40:08,420
Look.

541
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,958
"I'm dying.

542
00:40:13,959 --> 00:40:18,599
I hope to meet you before I die and tell you about your birth."

543
00:40:18,599 --> 00:40:20,160
Your birth?

544
00:40:22,520 --> 00:40:24,639
- Who wrote to you? 
 - I don't know.

545
00:40:24,639 --> 00:40:26,398
It was sent from the Phoenix Clan.

546
00:40:26,399 --> 00:40:28,599
Phoenix Clan?

547
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:30,559
The handwriting looks familiar.

548
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,678
I think it's Elder Dan Feng's.

549
00:40:32,679 --> 00:40:34,479
Elder Dan Feng?

550
00:40:35,959 --> 00:40:37,880
I must find her.

551
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:05,119
Qing Mu, what are you doing?

552
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,899
What demon are you?

553
00:41:06,899 --> 00:41:08,780
Why not show us your real appearance?

554
00:41:09,399 --> 00:41:11,079
Qing Mu, are you mad? What demon?

555
00:41:11,079 --> 00:41:12,500
I'm Feng Ran.

556
00:41:13,379 --> 00:41:15,878
Are you insane? Don't you know me?

557
00:41:15,879 --> 00:41:19,198
Jing Jian, don't be cheated by her.

558
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:33,000


559
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:43,980
 ♫ Year after year time goes by ♫ 

560
00:41:43,980 --> 00:41:50,859
 ♫ Don't be afraid if our fate comes back ♫ 

561
00:41:50,859 --> 00:41:57,379
 ♫ Rains flood and memories last ♫ 

562
00:41:57,379 --> 00:42:03,524
 ♫ My longing for you won't change no matter what ♫ 

563
00:42:03,524 --> 00:42:10,339
 ♫ I have been waiting for so many years ♫ 

564
00:42:10,339 --> 00:42:16,824
 ♫ I never leave despite endless sorrow ♫ 

565
00:42:16,824 --> 00:42:24,174
 ♫ Love is like a faraway bright moon ♫ 

566
00:42:24,175 --> 00:42:30,725
 ♫ I'll wait through my lifetime ♫ 

567
00:42:40,980 --> 00:42:48,019
 ♫ I spend years waiting for returning birds ♫ 

568
00:42:48,020 --> 00:42:54,399
 ♫ I never regret it and no one can replace you ♫ 

569
00:42:54,399 --> 00:43:01,679
 ♫ I hope we'll uncover the past when we wake up ♫ 

570
00:43:01,679 --> 00:43:08,680
 ♫ I'll finally bare my heart to you ♫ 

571
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:16,759
 ♫ Along the way, I watch flowers bloom and wither ♫ 

572
00:43:16,759 --> 00:43:23,639
 ♫ Maybe we'll meet and part again in the future ♫ 

573
00:43:23,639 --> 00:43:30,099
 ♫ Tears turn into clouds and rain falls in my heart ♫ 

574
00:43:30,100 --> 00:43:36,674
 ♫ When the clouds break, our future will be clear ♫ 

575
00:43:36,675 --> 00:43:47,025
 ♫ I'll enjoy a free life with you forever ♫ 

